{"tid":2354967,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重溫] 李加超：新疆反恐工作值得香港作為參考","createTime":"2021-01-06T00:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T01:29:06.000Z","uid":15010,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d3e205c10ce10dbe4c8052eed03dadf3ad9362e8","tid":2354967,"uid":15010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T00:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/li-16_lxYuA_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fli-16_lxYuA_1200x0.png&h=18226c9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">2019/1/9 </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n代表團考察期間，訪問了當地的反恐單位和警方設施，反恐戰術訓練中心、警察學校和邊景檢查站等，又與當地官員進行交流，行程中並不包括「職業技能培訓機構」。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員楊岳橋追問，新疆考察團是否看到當地有違反人權的措施時，李家超回答「沒有」，「我地所見到的全部都是以人權方式之類」，然後話鋒一轉，指此問題是戴上了「有色眼鏡」，稱<span class=\"red\">外訪選擇新疆，是因當地過去曾發生多宗恐襲，但近兩年情況「得以控制和改善」，故認為當地反恐工作值得香港作為參考，以制定反恐措施。</span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E8%80%83%E5%AF%9F%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E5%8F%8D%E6%81%90%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A/?fb_comment_id=2257031607664570_2636234903077570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2596%2586%25E8%2580%2583%25E5%25AF%259F%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%259C%258B%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%2F%3Ffb_comment_id%3D2257031607664570_2636234903077570&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGy8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=3ef9056b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2596%2586%25E8%2580%2583%25E5%25AF%259F%25E6%25